Valid values: [0.1, 1].

Default value: 0.3 (30%).', example='0.3'),
  maxGracefulTerminationSec?: int32(name='max_graceful_termination_sec', description='The maximum duration in seconds that `cluster-autoscaler` waits for Pods to terminate during a node drain for a scale-in event.

