Default value: `true`.', example='true'),
  keepInstanceName?: boolean(name='keep_instance_name', description='**[Deprecated]** Adding existing nodes during cluster creation is not supported. To add existing nodes to a cluster, first create a node pool and then call the [AttachInstancesToNodePool](https://help.aliyun.com/document_detail/2667920.html) API.

When using existing instances to create a cluster, whether to keep the instance names.

